These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, thai, colombian
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, family
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, october, august
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, fonseca, bluemaster
City: san-francisco, colone, hannover
There are 3 different favourite colors: orange, coral, azure
 1. the thai is on the left or right of the colombian##3
 2. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
 3. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 4. the thai is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 6. the person watching drama movies is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching documentary movies is the turkish##1
 8. the person who likes orange is the fonseca-smoker##1
 9. the colombian is between the fonseca-smoker and the person who likes azure##2
10. the person who likes orange is in an odd position##4
11. the person watching documentary movies is the bluemaster-smoker##1
12. the person watching family movies is the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |         2          |     3      |
| Nationality          | turkish   | colombian            | thai     |
| Movie-Genre           | documentary | family | drama |
| Birthday   | november      | august               | october        |
| Cigar           | bluemaster        | cain         | fonseca   |
| City         | hannover     | colone      | san-francisco       |
| Color     | azure        | coral              | orange       |

