.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-2::.
There are 3 different nationalities: french, italian, australian
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, puzzles, sudoku
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, cricket, weightlifting
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, blood-red, lilac
3 different games are played: canasta, whist, bridge
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, july, november
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 2. the french is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 3. the person who likes blood-red is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person who likes yellow##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's sport is rowing##2
 6. the person playing canasta is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's birthday is in june##2
 7. the australian is the person playing whist##1
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who likes lilac is the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |
| Nationality      | french | italian | australian        |
| Hobby          | puzzles   | sudoku    | singing        |
| Sport   | rowing    | cricket | weightlifting |
| Color   | lilac   | yellow  | blood-red         |
| Game           | bridge    | canasta | whist       |
| Birthday     | july   | november    | june  |

