.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, december, may
House: art-deco, futuristic, ranch-style
City: prague, new-york, miami
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, dunhill, havana
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, brown, emerald
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, roller, subway
 1. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
 2. the havana-smoker is the ranch-style house##1
 3. the person who likes brown is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the art-deco house is between the person traveling to new-york and the person driving the roller##2
 6. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who likes brown is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
 9. the havana-smoker is on the far right##1
10. the person traveling to miami is in an odd position##4
11. the person traveling to new-york is the dunhill-smoker##1
12. the person who likes brown is on the far left##1
13. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3       |
| Birthday      | december        | february     | may          |
| House          | futuristic     | art-deco | ranch-style    |
| City         | new-york    | prague  | miami |
| Cigar           | dunhill | old-henry    | havana    |
| Color   | brown      | emerald | fuchsia      |
| Transport           | van          | subway     | roller         |

