.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, purple, apricot
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, boat, bike
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, daisy, begonia
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, bluemaster, old-henry
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, scientist, librarian
City: miami, hannover, london
 1. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
 2. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 4. the old-henry-smoker is on the far right##1
 5. the havana-smoker is between the person traveling to hannover and the person driving the bike##2
 6. the scientist is on the far right##1
 7. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
 8. the person who growsbellflower is the person traveling to miami##1
 9. the paramedic is in an odd position##4
10. the librarian is in an even position##4
11. the scientist is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person driving the bike is the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Color      | purple  | apricot      | brown        |
| Transport         | bike   | ship     | boat |
| Flower   | bellflower | begonia | daisy     |
| Cigar   | bluemaster    | havana         | old-henry         |
| Job   | paramedic   | librarian     | scientist      |
| City         | miami  | london     | hannover         |

