.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-5::.
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, domino, monopoly
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, march, october
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, helicopter, quad-bike
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, bellflower, orchid
There 3 different types of food: apricot, lettuce, cucumber
House: ranch-style, wooden, art-deco
 1. the person driving the snowmobile is in an even position##4
 2. the person playing domino is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who growsorchid##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 5. the person eating apricot is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 7. the art-deco house is in the middle##1
 8. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 9. the person eating cucumber is between the person driving the helicopter and the person playing mah-jongg##2
10. the wooden house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |
| Game         | mah-jongg      | domino   | monopoly |
| Birthday           | october | january | march      |
| Transport   | quad-bike | snowmobile     | helicopter     |
| Flower   | lily   | bellflower      | orchid      |
| Food   | lettuce   | cucumber    | apricot   |
| House         | wooden       | art-deco    | ranch-style  |

