There 3 different types of food: apricot, pumpkin, cucumber
3 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, domino
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta
 1. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking coffee##2
 2. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
 3. the person who likes mauve is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person playing billiard is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 5. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 6. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 7. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person playing domino is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
10. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
12. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |
| City           | miami | hamburg | rome |
| Color   | chestnut  | ivory     | mauve    |
