 7. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1
 8. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 9. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
10. the person who growsrose is the person watching musical movies##1
11. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person who likes white##1
12. the person traveling to nizza is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| City      | hannover    | san-francisco   | nizza   |
| Color          | white    | coral    | lilac |
| Flower   | poppy       | rose   | azalea    |
| Cigar   | ritmeester    | blend | old-henry  |
| Movie-Genre           | disaster      | musical    | epic       |
| Hobby         | skydiving | collecting  | magic-tricks   |

