The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, subway, airplane
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, juice
City: new-york, hamburg, rome
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, aconite, bellflower
 1. the fan of salsa is the person who growsbellflower##1
 2. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
 3. the person drinking juice is the fonseca-smoker##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 5. the fan of funk is in an even position##4
 6. the fan of house is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
10. the person driving the subway is the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |
| Cigar          | chaman     | bolivar   | fonseca     |
| Music-Genre         | house | funk   | salsa  |
| Transport           | skateboard   | airplane | subway   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | soy-milk       | juice    |
| City   | rome        | new-york    | hamburg   |
| Flower         | aconite      | amaryllis     | bellflower |

 